EXPLOITABILITY: Moderate — Requires the application to use jQuery's DOM manipulation methods (`.html()`, `.append()`, `.parseHTML()`) on untrusted input. If the application sanitizes input before passing it to jQuery, the risk is mitigated, but the library version itself remains a vector.
